        <LI> Programming Guide in LaTeX/HTML/PDF
</td>
<td>-</td>
</tr>

<!---------------------------------------------------------------------->

<tr>
<td colspan="2">
<b>&nbsp;<p>Release 8.2.3: Performance</b>
</td>
<td valign="bottom"> Status </td>
</tr>
<tr><td colspan=3><hr></td></tr>

<tr>
<td width="3"></td>
<td>
        <LI> Enhance performance in HList, TList and Grid widgets.
</td>
<td>-</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td width="3"></td>
<td>
        <LI> Convert some C commands into ObjCmd's.
</td>
<td>-</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td width="3"></td>
<td>
        <LI> Bring Tix up to date with recent Tk developments to 
             support Unicode and internationalization.
</td>
<td>in progress</td>
</tr>

<!---------------------------------------------------------------------->

<tr>
<td colspan="2">
<b>&nbsp;<p>Release 8.3.0: Platform integration</b>
</td>
<td valign="bottom"> Status </td>
</tr>
<tr><td colspan=3><hr></td></tr>

<tr>
<td width="3"></td>
<td>
        <LI> Works with Tcl 8.4.
	<LI> Possibly drop support for static compile with itcl.
</td>
<td>-</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td width="3"></td>
<td>
        <LI> Drag-and-drop (pending TkDnD integration in the core?)
</td>
<td>-</td>
</tr>

<!---------------------------------------------------------------------->

<tr>
<td colspan="2">
<b>&nbsp;<p>Release 8.3.1: New features</b>
</td>
<td valign="bottom"> Status </td>
</tr>
<tr><td colspan=3><hr></td></tr>

<tr>
<td width="3"></td>
<td>
        <LI> Make the dirlist and dirtree widgets get their icons directly
             from the registry under windows, or from the MIME type
             under KDE or GNOME.
</td>
<td>-</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td width="3"></td>
<td>
        <LI> TEA2 compatible.
</td>
<td>-</td>
</tr>


